content: The ground truth BIRD region has been segmented with some inaccuracies. The prediction mask has some missing spots in the region.

The ground truth PERSON regions have been segmented with somewhat inaccurate boundaries and these tend to be under-segmented a bit, while the ground truth BICYCLE regions are over-extended towards the top. Some PERSON regions have been misclassified as BICYCLE and vice versa.

The region of the TRAIN is smaller in the prediction than in the ground truth, especially at the bottom left, where parts of the train are not detected. Also the boundary of the TRAIN is less accurate in the prediction, mainly in the bottom region.
The prediction has some internal regions that are incorrectly segmented as BACKGROUND. Also, it segments the TRAIN region at the bottom with a slightly irregular shape.

The ground truth BOAT regions have been segmented with imperfect boundaries and especially on the upper side of the bigger boat some regions have been over-extended. Also, the sail on top of the right boat is missing.

The ground truth PERSON region has been segmented with accurate boundaries, but the bottles on the background are completely missing from the prediction. Also, the leftmost arm holding the glass has been under-segmented. Some BACKGROUND areas that interact with the person have been misclassified as PERSON, especially on the top.

The prediction mask for the AEROPLANE in the center of the scene is missing the right wing. Moreover, the AEROPLANE on the top left of the scene is missing. The two PERSON regions on the bottom are incomplete and only partially predicted.
The prediction mask is quite chaotic, many SOFA regions have been hallucinated all over the scene, while the DOG and CHAIR regions have been coarsely segmented and are incomplete.

The prediction seems to capture most of the ground truth regions, but the MONITOR regions at the top of the scene have inaccurate boundaries. Specifically, the upper boundaries of the monitors are over-extended and the region between the two monitors, near the top, is not properly segmented.

The prediction captured the overall structure of the AEROPLANE, however, on the bottom right the prediction includes an additional AEROPLANE region that does not exist in the ground truth. Additionally, there are some details on the right of the AEROPLANE that are missed in the prediction.

The ground truth MONITOR region has been segmented with coarse boundaries. The prediction is even coarser and deviates in many points of the boundary with the ground truth, especially on the top and on the right. Additionally, the right border of the region on the prediction mask is very irregular.
The ground truth BOAT region has been segmented with incomplete boundaries. The prediction mask of the ground truth BOAT region on the center of the scene is incomplete, some details are missing.

The prediction mask has incorrectly classified the BOTTLE region on the left. Moreover, the DININGTABLE region in the prediction appears to be under-segmented at the center, near the top of the table.
The prediction TRAIN region has been segmented inaccurately, with noticeable gaps. It also spreads more towards the bottom and the right.
The prediction mask is generally accurate, but on the top and right sides, the PERSON region has been slightly over-segmented.
The ground truth AEROPLANE region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries and its shape is not correctly captured. Some parts, especially on the right, are missing.

The ground truth MOTORBIKE region on the left has been over-extended in the prediction, mostly towards the bottom of the region. Similarly, the ground truth PERSON region on the right has been slightly over-extended too. The MOTORBIKE region at the top right has been slightly under-segmented instead.

The ground truth BIRD region has been severely under-segmented. The BIRD region around the left-center and top-center parts of the image is missing. Also, the ground truth BIRD region on the bottom of the image has been over-extended to the right.

The prediction mask for the BOTTLE class is quite noisy and incomplete, missing pieces especially in the middle region and the bottom left. The right border is also jagged and inaccurate. Also, the ground truth PERSON region is somewhat coarsely segmented and under-segmented at the bottom.

The prediction mask is incomplete in many areas around the sheep. Noticeably, a large portion of the sheep towards the top left is missing, where it has been misclassified as BACKGROUND. Also, on both ears of the sheep a significant amount of pixels are missing, while the boundary between the sheep and the grass in the bottom is particularly flawed and coarse, with many missing pixels.

The ground truth TRAIN region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries and the lower region is over-extended. There's a region near the top-right corner that is missing in the ground truth but present in the prediction.
The ground truth CAT region has been segmented with relatively accurate boundaries. However, the prediction mask over-extends the bottom-right part of the region.

The predicted COW region on the right side of the scene has been misclassified, presenting many PERSON pixels, with an overall chaotic shape. Some PERSON regions on the left have been similarly affected, with COW pixels hallucinated nearby. The prediction mask is quite inaccurate.
The ground truth CAT region has been segmented with relatively accurate boundaries. However, the bottom boundary is a bit irregular in shape.
The prediction mask failed to capture the BICYCLE regions on the scene, as most of the BICYCLE has not been segmented at all. Furthermore, a small PERSON region has been hallucinated on the right.
The prediction mask has classified almost all pixels as CAT, with only a few background pixels correctly identified, especially around the top of the image.
The ground truth PERSON region has been segmented with imperfect boundaries and the region in the middle of the PERSON's torso is missing.
The prediction mask has rough, irregular boundaries and it is more extended than the ground truth MOTORBIKE region. Also, the prediction mask has multiple internal "holes".

The prediction mask of the ground truth BUS region is over-extended towards the bottom and boundaries are less defined compared to the ground truth. Also, the sign on the top of the bus is not well segmented.
The prediction mask of the PERSON regions on the left of the scene is incomplete. Also, some isolated POTTEDPLANT regions have been hallucinated on the top right of the building.

The prediction captured most of the ground truth regions. However, the ground truth COW regions near the left edge of the scene have been segmented with much coarser boundaries, and on the right side of the central COW region, these tend to be significantly over-extended.

The prediction mask is quite chaotic, many CHAIR regions have been hallucinated all over the scene, while the DININGTABLE region has been incomplete and often misclassified as CHAIR. The POTTEDPLANT on the top left is also missing from the prediction.
The prediction mask is missing a large portion of the SOFA region on the left of the scene, while on the top the remaining portion of the ground truth SOFA has been over-extended.

The prediction mask for the DOG region is inaccurate around the boundaries. The bottom regions of the DOG class have been misclassified as SOFA and GRASS, while the ground truth TVMONITOR region in the top has not been detected by the prediction.

The ground truth TRAIN region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries. The boundary has been over-extended towards the right. Some AEROPLANE regions have been hallucinated on the bottom left of the scene.

The ground truth BOAT region has been segmented with relatively coarse and imperfect boundaries, which appears to be over-extended. The prediction follows the same imperfection, while also hallucinating BOAT regions to the left, where there is probably only water.
The prediction mask is generally consistent with the ground truth, however, the left-most boundary of the TRAIN region has been over-extended towards the BACKGROUND.

The ground truth BUS region on the center of the scene has been segmented with mostly accurate boundaries, although the top part is slightly over-extended. The prediction BUS region is also a bit over-extended on the right.

The ground truth PERSON regions have been segmented with more accurate boundaries. The BACKGROUND/SOFA areas that interact with the PERSON regions have been misclassified as PERSON, especially near the bottom edges.

The ground truth CHAIR region on the right has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries that tend to be over-extended in the prediction. The PERSON region has been segmented with some inaccuracies, particularly on the right leg.

The prediction captured most of the ground truth regions. However, the ground truth BOAT region on the left of the scene is incomplete. The ground truth PERSON region on the top right of the scene has also been segmented coarsely, missing some details.

The prediction mask for the DININGTABLE has been under-segmented, particularly along its left edge. The CHAIR region has been incorrectly classified as PERSON and the PERSON regions have been incorrectly classified as CHAIR. The TENT on the upper right has been classified as PERSON.

The prediction mask of the ground truth MOTORBIKE region is largely incomplete, the area on the right side of the motorbike is missing. The prediction also struggles to reconstruct a complete shape, with holes all over. The ground truth PERSON region has been over-extended towards the right, misclassifying the region as PERSON.

The predicted PERSON regions have somewhat coarser boundaries. Additionally, there are some OBJECT regions towards the bottom-left which the prediction misclassified as DININGTABLE while the ground truth labels them as BACKGROUND. Finally, the CHAIR regions have been hallucinated inside the rightmost PERSON region.

The ground truth TVMONITOR region on the left has been segmented with imperfect boundaries, especially the top and bottom ones, while on the top right, regions of the background have been misclassified as POTTEDPLANT. Also, part of the PERSON region is missing.

The ground truth CAT region has been segmented with incomplete boundaries and on the top right its shape is irregular. In general the region is under-segmented, while the BACKGROUND area on the top left has been misclassified as CAT. Also the small region on the beam on the bottom has been only partially segmented.

The ground truth SOFA region on the top right has been covered by many AEROPLANE regions, similarly to what happens near the bottom right of the DOG region, while the background has been classified as SOFA, near the leftmost side of the dog region.

The prediction over-segments the HORSE region, especially around the left, top and right boundaries. The PERSON is under-segmented on the shoulders and slightly over-extended on the right side. Also, BACKGROUND areas around the HORSE and PERSON have been misclassified as HORSE.

The prediction mask is quite chaotic, the CHAIR region on the right has been expanded towards the center, while the DININGTABLE region has been hallucinated all over the scene. Also, the boundary between DININGTABLE and CHAIR regions is not clear.

The prediction has significantly over-segmented the HORSE region, especially on the top-right, where the BACKGROUND region has been misclassified as HORSE. Moreover, some of the background regions on the top and on the right have been classified as HORSE.
The ground truth SHEEP region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries. The prediction erroneously classifies parts of the sheep as CAT, DOG and COW.

The ground truth SHEEP region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries, especially the boundaries closer to the bottom of the image, where the prediction mask shows many regions that are severely under-segmented. Many BACKGROUND areas that interact with the SHEEP regions have been completely misclassified as SHEEP.

The prediction mask of the BOAT region is very noisy, especially in the upper portion of the image. The boundary regions of the BOAT region are severely over-extended, with many BACKGROUND pixels being misclassified as BOAT. Furthermore, there are some HOLES within the BOAT region.
The prediction mask is chaotic, many PERSON regions have been hallucinated all over the scene, while the MOTORBIKE region has been significantly under-segmented in the center.
The ground truth COW region has been misclassified as CAT. A small region within the COW has been misclassified as BOTTLE.
The BUS regions in the prediction mask are over-extended, especially on the bottom.

The prediction mask of the ground truth CAT region seems to have extended towards the top-left, with some artifacts being present in the top-left region outside the cat itself. Furthermore, the right boundary of the cat appears to have been truncated.

The prediction mask is quite chaotic, many PERSON regions have been hallucinated all over the scene, while the COW region has been segmented as a blend of PERSON, BICYCLE and HORSE. Furthermore, the COW region boundaries are very irregular.

The ground truth SHEEP region on the top has been significantly over-segmented by the prediction, and the background areas interacting with the region have been completely misclassified as SHEEP. In addition, a small region of the ground truth PERSON on the bottom left has been misclassified as BACKGROUND.

The ground truth CAT region on the center of the scene has been segmented with relatively accurate boundaries, except for regions on the bottom, where the object borders blend with the CAT stand borders. The prediction is chaotic, many CHAIR regions have been hallucinated in the left side of the CAT. Some parts of the CAT stand have been misclassified as CAT, especially on the bottom.

The prediction captured the overall AEROPLANE region, but the boundaries tend to be slightly over-extended especially near the tail and some parts of the fuselage. Some BACKGROUND regions have been misclassified as AEROPLANE in the top-left corner, and some AEROPLANE regions have been misclassified as BACKGROUND close to the tail of the aeroplane.

The ground truth CAT region has been segmented with imperfect boundaries and holes, especially the two gaps near the left edge and the top right edge. The ground truth PERSON region has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries on the right side. Some parts of the CHAIR have been misclassified as CAT.
The prediction BOAT region is over-extended vertically at the top. The PERSON region is missing in the prediction mask. The BOAT region's boundaries show coarse, irregular segmentation.

The predicted CAT region on the top left of the scene is under-segmented, also, some of the background in between the glasses has been misclassified as BOTTLE. Also, the predicted BOTTLE mask is over-extended and covers some regions that belong to the CAT.

The ground truth BOTTLE region on the center of the scene has been segmented with inaccurate boundaries. The lower parts are under-segmented a bit. In the prediction, the upper part of the BOTTLE region has been severely truncated and deformed.

The prediction mask is quite noisy: many SOFA regions have been hallucinated all over the PERSON region, while PERSON regions have been hallucinated into the SOFA region, especially on the right. Overall, the boundaries of PERSON are inaccurate, and the segmentation is noisy.

The prediction mask is quite chaotic. The ground truth DOG region on the center of the scene has been segmented with many inaccuracies, and many CHAIR regions have been hallucinated all over the DOG region. Also, some PERSON regions are mixed with the DOG.

The prediction mask is mostly correct, but some of the boundaries are not smooth and less accurate, especially on the cow's right side. Also the region at the bottom of the mask is slightly over-segmented.

The ground truth CAR region on the right of the scene has been segmented with less, coarser, boundaries. On the other hand, in the prediction, the CAR region has been hallucinated, so its shape is quite different from that of the ground truth, especially on the right.
The prediction mask is quite chaotic, many POTTEDPLANT regions have been hallucinated all over the scene, while the DININGTABLE region has been mixed with CHAIR regions.
The prediction mask of the ground truth BOTTLE region is quite coarse, missing some details, while the BOTTLE region on the bottom right has been over-extended towards the bottom.

The prediction mask is overall accurate, but it exhibits some errors. The DOG region in the center of the scene presents some patches of SHEEP at its front and on the back, while the dog nose is not present.

The ground truth DININGTABLE region has been heavily under-segmented, the upper CHAIR regions near the upper corners have been merged with the DININGTABLE region, and the leftmost CHAIR region on the left edge has been merged with the DININGTABLE region too.
The PERSON regions have been over-extended especially around the boundaries, while the DININGTABLE region is incomplete at the top.

The prediction mask is quite chaotic. The SHEEP regions on the left have been inaccurately classified as COW, with a small region classified as SHEEP again. The ground truth DOG region has been completely misclassified as COW. Furthermore, many GRASS regions have been hallucinated in the regions where the PERSON region is segmented.
The prediction has segmented the PERSON region overall well, but there is a part near the bottom-left edge of the image that is incorrectly classified as PERSON.
The prediction only captured the center of the ground truth SOFA region, with significant under-segmentation on the top, left and right sides.

The ground truth AEROPLANE region has some holes in it, in particular, the center and the top are missing some parts. The ground truth PERSON region in the center is under-segmented a bit. The connection between the PERSON class and the AEROPLANE class is segmented as AEROPLANE class.

The ground truth PERSON region on the left is incomplete, while the prediction mask covers it entirely, even extending slightly outside of it. Additionally, the prediction segmented the POTTEDPLANT regions further to the right with significant inaccuracy.

The ground truth PERSON region on the top is missing some details and the prediction fails to capture them. The boundary between CAR and PERSON is not well defined on the prediction mask. Furthermore, the prediction has hallucinated PERSON regions where there is CAR in the ground truth, especially on the top-left.

The ground truth CAT region has been segmented with slightly inaccurate boundaries and the CAT region is under-segmented a bit on the top. The BACKGROUND areas that interact with the CAT region have been completely misclassified as CAT.

The prediction mask of the TRAIN region appears to be incomplete and has irregular boundaries, especially towards the rightmost region of the train. Moreover, the details of the shape of the front of the train are not captured well. Some regions outside the train have also been misclassified as TRAIN.

The prediction of the CHAIR region on the left is quite chaotic, it appears to be over-extended with rough boundaries. The PERSON region on the right is also poorly segmented with a coarse boundary, and the lower half of it seems incomplete. Furthermore, the SOFA region on the bottom right has been significantly misclassified as CHAIR and BACKGROUND, resulting in a highly irregular shape.
The prediction captured the general shape of the AEROPLANE, but the boundaries are rough and tend to be overly extended.

The ground truth COW region has been segmented incompletely, the predicted mask only contains the larger cow and a fragment of the smaller cow. The last COW ground truth region has been segmented, but only with its boundary. Finally, some PERSON ground truth regions are completely missed.

The prediction captured the general shape of the AEROPLANE, but has inaccurate boundaries. Some portions of the aircraft are missing, while some BACKGROUND areas have been misclassified as AEROPLANE, especially on the bottom-left part, and the wingtips. Also, some "holes" appear, classified as BOAT class.

The ground truth SHEEP regions have been segmented with inaccurate boundaries and the region to the right has been over-extended towards the bottom. The BACKGROUND areas surrounding the sheep on the right has been misclassified as SHEEP.
The BUS region on the right is over-segmented, extending downwards towards the bottom-right corner of the scene. Also, the ground truth BUS region on the top has been segmented coarsely.

The prediction mask of the PERSON region on the center of the scene is missing some details especially around the left edge and on the back. The prediction also hallucinated BACKGROUND regions inside the ground truth BOTTLE region on the bottom-right, while the BOTTLE region itself is missing portions.
The prediction mask captured most of the ground truth regions, but the POTTEDPLANT region has been roughly segmented. Also, some BOTTLE regions have been hallucinated at the center of the scene.
The prediction captured the main regions of the ground truth BIRD, however, the leftmost wing has been under-segmented.

The prediction mask is noisy and incomplete. In the ground truth mask, most of the BOAT regions on the top left and right of the scene have been segmented with a more complete and defined shape, whereas these regions are either partially segmented or not segmented at all in the prediction mask. There are also many regions of the ground truth that are not classified correctly in the prediction, such as the bridge in the center left.
The prediction mask is very sparse and incomplete; the SOFA region is under-segmented, with the central region completely missed.
The prediction mask of the ground truth BICYCLE region has been over-extended towards the top right, on the handlebar and back tire. It has also been overextended on the lower part of the front tire.

The prediction mostly overlaps with the ground truth CAT region, but it has extended a bit towards the upper right side and has some coarse and irregular boundaries, while the CAT region on the lower left side has been segmented with incorrect boundaries and the adjacent BACKGROUND areas have been misclassified as CAT.
The predicted BICYCLE regions are generally over-extended compared to the ground truth, merging the two bicycles and blurring their boundaries.
The predicted BOTTLE region in the scene is significantly over-segmented, with large portions of the PERSON, DININGTABLE classes, and even BACKGROUND being misclassified.
